A. Service Workflows
To inform the functional requirements of the proposed CRM system, the following sample
workflows illustrate how KASNEB currently handles stakeholder interactions related to customer
enquiries, complaints, and service requests.
These workflows are not exhaustive but represent the core case-handling and escalation
processes expected to be supported by the CRM.
The listed workflows are indicative and based on customer service touchpoints analyzed during
the initial scoping.
The successful bidder will be required to conduct a comprehensive business process analysis
across all relevant departments
