⮚ Once approved, CRM notifies the stakeholder
and updates case status.
⮚ If necessary, CRM triggers an update to the ERP
(e.g. to record a deferral or issue a certificate).
8. If request is incomplete or invalid:
⮚ Officer updates the case with the reason and
may request additional information from the
